(136, '_transient_dash_5438fb5baf31c513fff2b9a1067656a6', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://cn.wordpress.org/2015/12/13/clifford/''>WordPress 4.4“Clifford”</a> <span class="rss-date">2015年12月12日</span><div class="rssSummary">WordPress 4.4简体中文版现已开放下载，或在您的WordPress仪表盘中升级。我们将此版本命名为“ [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/in-case-you-missed-it-issue-6''>WPTavern: In Case You Missed It – Issue 6</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/features-as-plugins-first-transitions-into-features-as-projects''>WPTavern: Features-as-Plugins First Transitions Into Features-as-Projects</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/bbpress-2-6-expected-later-this-year-two-major-features-pushed-back-to-2-7''>WPTavern: bbPress 2.6 Expected Later This Year, Two Major Features Pushed Back to 2.7</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>热门插件:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-analytics-dashboard-for-wp/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>Google Analytics Dashboard for WP</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=google-analytics-dashboard-for-wp&amp;_wpnonce=2b6e3badb8&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Google Analytics Dashboard for WP''>安装</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
